crazy english is a 1999 chinese documentary directed by zhang yuan . the film premiered along with zhang 's seventeen years at the 1999 locarno international film festival . it established zhang 's position as a " legitimate " director after years of working independently from , and often at odds with , the chinese authorities . in contrast to earlier films , like east palace , west palace ( 1997 ) , crazy english was produced with the cooperation of the state-owned xi'an film studio , which enjoys a " presented by " billing in the film 's credits .